'''Pablo García Pérez de Lara''' (yavutse 29 Ukwakira, 1970), ni umunya Esipanye ukora ndetse akandika filimi . <ref>https://www.pablogarciaperezdelara.com/</ref> Azwi cyane nkumuyobozi wa documentaire nyafurika z''izwi cyane'' nka Tchindas. <ref>https://letterboxd.com/director/pablo-garcia-perez-de-lara/</ref> <ref>https://mubi.com/cast/pablo-garcia-perez-de-lara</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse mu 1970 i Barcelona, [[Esipanye|Espanye]] . Yize muri Centre d'Estudis Cinematogràfics de Catalunya (CECC).<ref>https://www.llenguadesignes.com/</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Mu 1996, yatangiye gukina bwa mbere muri firime ''Fuente Álamo, Caress of Time nkimpano'' yumushinga watanzwe na Barcelona Alternativa festival. Yarangije filime muri 2001 hanyuma ahitamo muri SEMINCI muri Valladolid. Filime yari yatoranijwe kumugaragaro muri Karlovy Vary. Hanyuma muri 2007, yakoze firime ''Butterfly'' ikora igice cyemewe cya Karlovy Vary na San Sebastián.<ref>https://www.documentamadrid.com/en/films/camino-incierto</ref> <ref name="africanfilmny">https://africanfilmny.org/directors/pablo-garcia-perez-de-lara/</ref> Muri 2015, yakoze documentaire yamamaye cyane ''Tchindas'' afatanya na Marc Serena . Yatoranijwe mu birori mpuzamahanga bya firime kandi yegukana ibihembo 14 mpuzamahanga. Film nyuma yatsinze Outfest 's Grand Jury Award for Excellence mu sinema.<ref>https://pro.festivalscope.com/film/tchindas</ref> <ref>https://variety.com/2015/film/news/outfest-2015-winners-list-1201543695/</ref>

Mu 2002, yakoze filime ngufi ''Alicia Portrayed'' yatoranijwe muri Cannes Festival's Critics 'Week 2003.  Hagati aho, Pablo yakoze documentaire ebyiri ''Son de Galicia'' muri 2006 na ''Mura, un poble de cine'' muri 2010 kuri tereviziyo. Nyuma yaje gukora nka ''cinemateri wa'' documentaire Familystrip yamenyekanye cyane muri 2009. Muri 2011, yakoze documentaire ''Oblidant a Nonot'' . Yakiriye igihembo cya City of Alcalá muri Alcine 2011, ndetse nigihembo cyabateze amatwi muri l'Alternativa de Barcelona 2011 na Filime ngufi nziza mu rurimi rw'amarenga muri Cinemobile de Sevilla 2011. Noneho muri 2012, yabaye umukinnyi wa ''cinemateri wa film El efecto K. El montador de Stalin'' yerekanwe mumunsi mukuru 60 mpuzamahanga kwisi. <ref>http://catalanfilms.cat/es/profesionales/pablo-garcia-perez-de-lara</ref><ref>https://moviefit.me/persons/229763-pablo-garcia-perez-de-lara</ref>

